title: Senators Coons, Baldwin recognize National Manufacturing Day on Senate Floor (Christopher A Coons)
text: ( Source : Christopher A Coons) FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE: Friday, October 2, 2015 CONTACT: Sean Coit at 202-224-5042 or Sean_Coit@coons.senate.gov U.S. Senators Chris Coons (D-Del.) and Tammy Baldwin (D-Wis.) yesterday spoke on the Senate floor
